title: Buntha discusses navigating language barriers in the hospital

media:group.media:title: Buntha discusses navigating language barriers in the hospital
media:group.media:description:
Buntha, a participant in our “Being Asian in America” documentary, discusses navigating language barriers in the hospital after he had a severe head injury at work. 

This video is part of our “Being Asian in America” project. 
Watch the full documentary here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LIIvqJDv6_4 
For more on the project, visit https://www.pewresearch.org/BeingAsianInAmerica
